![Burning145.jpg](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1600903567723-AJDWKV262V2VJE1ZJI7L/Burning145.jpg)

This past weekend was Batman Day! (Sep 19th) To celebrate we decided to talk the latest and greatest stories that changed the way we look at Batman today. Whether it be Golden Age, Silver Age, or Modern-day comics, video game franchises, or live-action films, Batman has some of the greatest stories of any comic book character ever. Join us as we gush over some of the best stories ever printed, by some of the heaviest hitters in the comic industry, and try our best to nail what makes Batman so popular!  
**  
